1. DESCRIPTION:

	this is my emacs config for emacs 24

you can get emacs 24 from git version system

home page: http://savannah.gnu.org/projects/emacs/#


the URL of git: http://savannah.gnu.org/git/?group=emacs



	# git clone git://git.savannah.gnu.org/emacs.git

	# cd emacs

	# ./configure

	# make

	# sudo make install



2. INSTALL:

	# git clone git@github.com:liugang/galen-emacs.git

	# mv .emacs.d{,-bak}

	# mv galen-emacs ~/.emacs.d

	# cd ~/.emacs.d

	# make




start your emacs
